<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bḥnwṭ wạ̉ṭyạb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bḥnwṭ wbạ̉ṭyạb jỷnạ mn ạ̉jl jsd ạlḥbyb
 ḥzn qlb wdmʿ ʿyn lạ tbrḥ ạlfkr dẖkry̱ ạlṣlyb
 hdẖạ nwrhạ mlạk yạlh mn mnẓr ʿjyb
 ạlqrạr- qạm rby qạm mntṣraⁿạ qạm ḥqaⁿ̃ạ qạm bạlẓfr
 wbmwth wqyạmth ytrnm qlby bạlfrḥ
 flswf ạ̉sẖdw bnṣrth wlswf ạ̉ḥyạ bqwth
 wlswf ạ̉htf llạbd qạm rby qạm bạlẓfr
 2- bạlạ̉frạḥ wbạlsrwr nzf tlk ạlbsẖry̱ llạ̉nạm
 qạm rby bạlḥq qạm lạ slṭẗ llmwt wạlậlạm
 ạ̹dẖ bạlmwt dạs ạlmwt mạnḥaⁿạ ạlʿtq wạlslạm
 3- sẖkr qlby mdy̱ ḥyạty ạ̉hdy lmn fdạny bdmạh
 lw lm tkn tlk ạldmạʾ lknt hạlkaⁿạ wlạ njạẗ
 lknh bʿd mwt qạm wạhbaⁿạ ly ạlḥyạẗ</lyrics>
